    "description": "Complete test collection for the Blog Engine REST API.\n\n**How to use:**\n1. Set the `base_url` variable to your server (default: http://localhost:8080).\n2. Run **Login as Admin** or **Login as User** — the token is saved automatically.\n3. All authenticated requests use the saved token via the `{{admin_token}}` or `{{user_token}}` variables.\n4. Run **Create Post** before testing Update/Delete Post — the post ID is saved automatically.\n5. Run **Create Comment** before testing Update/Delete Comment — the comment ID is saved automatically.\n\n**All seeded users share the same password:** `1234`",
